headline: From AI Darlings To Dow Dinosaurs: Investors Flee Software For Old-Economy Stocks
summary: Software stocks are sliding as AI disruption fears grow, but investors aren't panicking. Goldman Sachs shows capital rotating toward AI-insulated, real-economy sectors.

headline: A Look At LyondellBasell (LYB) Valuation After Capacity Cuts And Better Than Expected Results
summary: LyondellBasell Industries (LYB) is back in focus after its third quarter 2025 results exceeded expectations, with management outlining multi year ethylene capacity closures and idling aimed at rebalancing supply and supporting sector pricing.
